text: József Csatári (17 December 1943 – 30 January 2021) was a Hungarian wrestler. He was born in Budapest. He was Olympic bronze medalist in Freestyle wrestling in 1968 and in 1972. He won a silver medal at the 1970 World Wrestling Championships. Csatári died on 30 January 2021 at the age of 77.Gyász: elhunyt Csatári József kétszeres olimpiai bronzérmes birkózó ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Hungary Category:Hungarian wrestlers Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
